witter":null,"created":1525449900,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/690d/f45a/314308_mini.png?m=1558593537","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/690d/f45a/314308_mini.png?m=1558593537","location":null,"btc":null,"id":314308},"last_reply_by":"HFX3389","last_touched":1616723417,"title":"你们的城市禁摩，电了吗 ？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/765253","created":1616721469,"content":"东莞这几天在禁摩，禁电，直接入村里搜车。。。。\r\n\r\n吓得我不敢开摩托车上班。。。\r\n\r\n民声大怨。。。。。\r\n\r\n你们的城市禁了没？\r\n\r\n\r\n![lADPBFuNdMPu1mnNAyDNAhY_534_800.jpg_720x720q90g.jpg]( https://i.loli.net/2021/03/26/eTJS2hCfQoHOBWY.jpg)","content_rendered":"<p>东莞这几天在禁摩，禁电，直接入村里搜车。。。。</p>\n<p>吓得我不敢开摩托车上班。。。</p>\n<p>民声大怨。。。。。</p>\n<p>你们的城市禁了没？</p>\n<p><img alt=\"lADPBFuNdMPu1mnNAyDNAhY_534_800.jpg_720x720q90g.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.loli.net/2021/03/26/eTJS2hCfQoHOBWY.jpg\"/></p>\n","last_modified":1616721469,"replies":13,"id":765253},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1616603305","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1616603305","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":43917,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1616603305","stars":7308,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"username":"cherbim","website":"","github":null,"psn":null,"avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6815/1470/287076_mini.png?m=1519464408","bio":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/cherbim","tagline":"v2ex垃圾用户一名！","twitter":null,"created":1517027646,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6815/1470/287076_mini.png?m=1519464408","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6815/1470/287076_mini.png?m=1519464408","location":"","btc":null,"id":287076},"last_reply_by":"bianzhifu","last_touched":1616035252,"title":"举报 server 酱私自调用 api 发广告行为","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/765309","created":1616726512,"content":"前段时间，因为可能要外派支援 xj，就试着远离 tg，准备使用微信推送接口，曾经体验用了一下 server 酱，后来觉得频率有限制，就放弃了，后来自己撸一个，利用 cf 反代企业微信应用推送到微信，然后就没用 server 酱了，今天突然收到一条方糖推送日记提醒消息，如下图，server 酱竟然私自调用我的 api 接口，这操作也太下饭了，没有经过我的允许，大半夜私自调用我的的 api 接口，给用户推送广告，如图：\r\n\r\n![]( https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/03/26/6X5gM9.jpg)\r\n\r\n特意去官网看了下，确实没有删除个人 key 的地方，如图，我当时只是网页测试了一下，我以为是临时性的，他竟然记录我的 key，还发广告，我还找不到删除的地方，我全部设置空白保存提示无法保存，最后还是去企业微信把应用 Secret 改了吧，\r\n![]( https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/03/26/6XIAZq.jpg)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n讲个更恐怖的事：我的是企业应用，是为多人服务的，我当时测试是推送给所有人，然后 server 酱直接把广告推送给所有人了，而且那个广告链接，这个连个授权都没有，用户只要点击链接就可以获得 sendkey，任何用户都可以利用 sendkey 直接推送任何消息，\r\n\r\n下图为其他账号接受的信息（点击查看详情可以直接看到 sendkey 信息）：\r\n\r\n![]( https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/03/26/6XT156.jpg)\r\n\r\n附上原本推送广告信息:\r\n\r\n~~~\r\n🎈 方糖推送日记提醒\r\n📖 来写日记吧\r\n\r\n<a href='https://sct.ftqq.com/auto/a8fb33eb25d7a45e562d19ccae81a6c3'>去 Server 酱查看详情</a>\r\n~~~\r\n\r\n**珍爱生命，原理 server 酱****","content_rendered":"<p>前段时间，因为可能要外派支援 xj，就试着远离 tg，准备使用微信推送接口，曾经体验用了一下 server 酱，后来觉得频率有限制，就放弃了，后来自己撸一个，利用 cf 反代企业微信应用推送到微信，然后就没用 server 酱了，今天突然收到一条方糖推送日记提醒消息，如下图，server 酱竟然私自调用我的 api 接口，这操作也太下饭了，没有经过我的允许，大半夜私自调用我的的 api 接口，给用户推送广告，如图：</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/03/26/6X5gM9.jpg\"/></p>\n<p>特意去官网看了下，确实没有删除个人 key 的地方，如图，我当时只是网页测试了一下，我以为是临时性的，他竟然记录我的 key，还发广告，我还找不到删除的地方，我全部设置空白保存提示无法保存，最后还是去企业微信把应用 Secret 改了吧，\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/03/26/6XIAZq.jpg\"/></p>\n<p>讲个更恐怖的事：我的是企业应用，是为多人服务的，我当时测试是推送给所有人，然后 server 酱直接把广告推送给所有人了，而且那个广告链接，这个连个授权都没有，用户只要点击链接就可以获得 sendkey，任何用户都可以利用 sendkey 直接推送任何消息，</p>\n<p>下图为其他账号接受的信息（点击查看详情可以直接看到 sendkey 信息）：</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/03/26/6XT156.jpg\"/></p>\n<p>附上原本推送广告信息:</p>\n<pre><code>🎈 方糖推送日记提醒\n📖 来写日记吧\n\n&lt;a href='https://sct.ftqq.com/auto/a8fb33eb25d7a45e562d19ccae81a6c3'&gt;去 Server 酱查看详情&lt;/a&gt;\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>珍爱生命，原理 server 酱</strong>**</p>\n","last_modified":1616726512,"replies":12,"id":765309},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3c59/dc04/21_large.png?m=1598508742","name":"shenzhen","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3c59/dc04/21_normal.png?m=1598508742","title":"深圳","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/shenzhen","topics":2086,"footer":"","header":"","title_alternative":"Shenzhen","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3c59/dc04/21_mini.png?m=1598508742","stars":1493,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":21,"parent_node_name":"cn"},"member":{"username":"lvgsnm","website":null,"github":null,"psn":null,"avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/710a5d5104b8c685d2251a221ce0904b?s=24&d=retro","bio":null,"url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/lvgsnm","tagline":null,"twitter":null,"created":1586843401,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/710a5d5104b8c685d2251a221ce0904b?s=24&d=retro","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/710a5d5104b8c685d2251a221ce0904b?s=24&d=retro","location":null,"btc":null,"id":483541},"last_reply_by":"lvgsnm","last_touched":1616744120,"title":"深圳房票咨询","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/765407","created":1616741566,"content":"广东省外户口，深圳无房，外省有房有贷 1 套(纯商贷，未还清，正在还)， 深圳社保已满 5 年未中断\r\n问题：在深圳购房的话，假如只用公积金贷款，其余全付现款，首付要几成？（找了 2 个中介，一个说三成，一个说五成，不知道到底是几成）","content_rendered":"广东省外户口，深圳无房，外省有房有贷 1 套(纯商贷，未还清，正在还)， 深圳社保已满 5 年未中断<br />问题：在深圳购房的话，假如只用公积金贷款，其余全付现款，首付要几成？（找了 2 个中介，一个说三成，一个说五成，不知道到底是几成）","last_modified":1616741607,"replies":11,"id":765407},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1616560311","name":"career","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.png?m=1616560311","title":"职场话题","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","topi